Class HyperbolicActivationLayer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.lang.NNLayer
      • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.layers.java.HyperbolicActivationLayer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class HyperbolicActivationLayer
extends NNLayer
    This activation layer uses a parameterized hyperbolic function. This function, ion various parameterizations, can resemble: x^2, abs(x), x^3, x However, at high +/- x, the behavior is nearly linear.
